Did you know that Greek Yogurt is a low lactose food? It contains about 2/3 less lactose than whole milk and the probiotics and live cultures also help you digest it—not to mention it’s a great source of protein (some are 16 grams per serving!)—so if you’re sensitive to lactose, like I am, then give plain Greek yogurt a try and see what happens! I always recommend plain yogurt because MOST flavored yogurts have lots of added sugar. #cleaneating #protein #greekyogurt #foodfacts #healthyfoodfacts #guthealth #healthyeatingtips

Sharing my top tip for how I healed my gut, cured my SIBO (small intestinal bacterial overgrowth) and lost 20 pounds in the last year—which was by significant reducing my consumption of ultra processed foods (think cereal, candy, sodas, and most pre packaged items) and swapped them out for whole foods like fruits, vegetables, seafood, meat, eggs etc! #guthealth #guthealing #digestion #sibo #healthylifestyle #healthyfood #cleaneating #wholefoods #diet #nutrition

My go to weekly smoothie! I recently switched to using collagen in my smoothies instead of protein powder per my nutritionists recommendation, as many protein powders contain added sugars and other unnecessary ingredients like gums that are difficult to digest and can cause bloating. @furtherfood chocolate collagen is my favorite right now—it’s super smooth and creamy! I highly recommend giving it a try and they shared a promo code for my followers to use THEFOODJOY 🤗 #smoothie #cleaneating #guthealth #healthyrecipes #collagen #protein #proteinsmoothie #smoothierecipe
—
1 frozen banana
1/4 cup frozen raspberries
Pinch organic cinnamon
2 scoops chocolate Further Food collagen
1 scoop raw cacao powder
1/2 teaspoon organic raw unfiltered honey
2 tablespoons raw almond butter
1/2 cup unsweetened organic coconut milk

The PERFECT ratio of just 4 ingredients to make the best overnight oats:
-1/2 cup organic oats
-1/4 cup yogurt
-1/2 cup milk of choice (I used almond)
-1/2 teaspoon organic maple syrup
This is your go to base then you can flavor from there! I added cinnamon and a handful of frozen raspberries to mine! Save for later and share with a friend 😉 #overnightoats #healthyrecipes #healthyrecipe #cleaneating #cleanrecipes #breakfastideas
